    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <note>The following incipit and explicit are taken from <ref type="mss" corresp="BAVet149"/>, quoted according to
                    the catalogue description in <bibl><ptr target="bm:GrebTiss1935Codices"/><citedRange unit="page">576-577</citedRange></bibl>.</note>
                <div type="textpart" subtype="title" xml:lang="gez">
                    <ab> 
                        በስመ፡ አብ፡ <gap reason="ellipsis"/> ድርሳን፡ ዘቅዱስ፡ ገብርኤል<supplied reason="omitted">፡</supplied> ሊቀ፡ መላእክት፡ ዘይትነበብ፡ አመ፡
                        ፲ወ፱ለየካቲት፨ ወሶበ፡ ተፈጸመ፡ መዋዕለ፡ ፅንሳ፡ ወለደቶ፡ ለዮሐንስ፡ ካህን፡ ወነቢይ፡ ወ<surplus>ወ</surplus>መጥምቅ፡ ወዝ፡ ውእቱ፡ 
                        ገብርኤ<supplied reason="omitted">ል፡</supplied> <sic>ዘተፈነዎ፡</sic> እምኀበ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ አብ፡ 
                        <supplied reason="omitted">ኀበ፡</supplied> ማርያም፡ ቅድስት<supplied reason="omitted">፡</supplied> ድንግል፨ ወላዲተ፡ አምላጅ፡ ከመ፡
                        ይዜንዋ፡ <surplus>ንዋ፡</surplus> ተሠግዎቶ፡ ለወልደ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ ሕያው<supplied reason="omitted">፡</supplied> እምኔሃ፡
                        <surplus>ወ</surplus>በሳድስ፡ ወርኅ፡ እም<surplus>፡ </surplus>አመ፡ ዜነዎ፡ ለዘካር<supplied reason="omitted">ያ</supplied>ስ፡ ልደተ፡ ዮሐንስ፨
                    </ab>
                </div>
                <div type="textpart" subtype="explicit" xml:lang="gez">
                    <ab>
                        በአሐቲ፡ ሰን<add place="interlinear">በ</add>ት፡ ወመንፈቀ፡ ሰንበት፡ 
                        <choice><corr resp="bm:GrebTiss1935Codices">ይሥዕር፡</corr><sic>ይሥዓር፡</sic></choice> 
                        መስዋዕተ፡ <sic>ወመጻሕፍት፡</sic> ወያማስን፡ 
                        <choice><corr resp="bm:GrebTiss1935Codices">ርኵሶሙ፡</corr><sic>ርኩሶሙ፡</sic></choice>
                        በውስተ፡ መቅደስ፡ እስከ፡ ማኅለቅተ፡ ዓመታት፡ ይትወሀብ፡ እድሜሁ፡ ለሙስና፨ በረከተ፡ ጸሎቱ፡ <gap reason="ellipsis"/>
                    </ab>
                </div>
            </div>
